{"article_id":"uJzatBqs1rRHUxgn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Watch CNN and NY1 's Democratic debate ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"moderated by Wolf Blitzer ,","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Thursday , April 14 at 9 p.m . ET .","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"Milwaukee","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"( CNN )","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Two candidates","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"vying to take down their parties ' front-runners","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"could get big boosts","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"if they win Tuesday in Wisconsin .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Texas Sen. Ted Cruz is leading Donald Trump in the Badger State 's polls .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"And a Bernie Sanders win would mark his sixth victory over Hillary Clinton in the last seven states","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"to vote .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"It 's the last big test until April 19 ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and each candidate has a lot to win","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"- or lose .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Wisconsin is the first electoral test","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"of whether he 's paying a price .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Trump 's campaign says","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"it 's expecting a close race in Wisconsin .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"It 's `` a toss-up , ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"senior adviser Barry Bennett told CNN .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"But the polls show Cruz with a 10-point lead in Wisconsin","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"-- and","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"if that margin grows Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"it 'd be a sign","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"that the controversies","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"swirling around Trump 's campaign","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"are taking their toll .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"`` I really believe","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"tomorrow were going to have a very , very big victory .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Very very big , ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"I 've been up here a lot .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"And I love it , and the people","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"I love . ''","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"If Cruz wins ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"it would make Trump 's path to 1,237 delegates before the Republican National Convention precarious .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"In a tight three-way race , he has little room for error , even with east coast states","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Trump should win up next .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"It 's made more complicated by Cruz 's mastery of the intricate rules and details of the nominating process","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"-- which has left Trump crying foul","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and threatening lawsuits in states like Louisiana ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"where Cruz netted 10 more delegates than Trump","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"even though Trump won the state .","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"`` His team does n't understand how these processes work","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"so","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"any time they lose","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"they scream ,","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"'The election 's been stolen from us , ' ''","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"Cruz said Monday on WISN radio in Wisconsin .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"`` It 's just silliness . ''","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"A loss would dent Trump .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"But it would crush Cruz ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"who has retail politicked his way across the Badger State","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"as if it were Iowa in recent weeks .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"While Trump is trying to claim a national movement ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Cruz is waging a state-by-state , delegate-by-delegate knife fight","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to keep Trump from clinching the GOP nomination .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"He 'll try to pick up 42 more in Wisconsin :","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"18","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"that go to the statewide winner ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"plus 24 more","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"chosen three apiece by the state 's eight congressional districts .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Part of Wisconsin 's importance to Cruz is that the calendar soon shifts to shakier ground for him .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"He 's favored in the winner-take-all South Dakota , Montana and Nebraska contests ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"but could lose big in the next contest on the calendar , New York on April 19 , and then Maryland , Pennsylvania , Connecticut , Rhode Island and Delaware the following week .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"`` Just a couple of weeks ago , all of the media commentators were saying","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Wisconsin was a state","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"that I could not compete","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"and do well , ''","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"Cruz said Monday in Kenosha .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"`` They were saying","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"it was a state","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that was a natural state for Donald Trump .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"The state historically has been a purple or even a blue state at times .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"It 's a state","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"that is ,","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"that is very heavily based on manufacturing ,","depth":16},{"id":79,"text":"that has a lot of union members and working class members .","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"Supposedly , it was Donald Trump 's sweet spot ,","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"and yet I think","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"the people of Wisconsin , they 're looking at the records of the candidates ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"and they realize","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"that Donald screams","depth":18},{"id":85,"text":"and yells a lot ,","depth":18},{"id":86,"text":"but he has no solutions . ''","depth":17},{"id":87,"text":"JUST WATCHED Clinton , Sanders get testy before Wisconsin primary","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Clinton , Sanders get testy before Wisconsin primary 04:16","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"He was swept in the South , and bloodied in the Rust Belt .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"when the race shifted West ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Bernie Sanders won five out of six states ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"regaining his footing","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"and bolstering his argument","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"to take the race all the way through the last contests on June 7 .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"A win in Wisconsin would give him a significant boost","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"just as the race heads to New York","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"-- the state","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"where he was born ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"and which Clinton represented in the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"It would also give him victories in six out of the seven states in the month","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"leading up to it --","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"helping to fuel the passion and small-dollar donations","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"driving his candidacy .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Win or lose ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Sanders ' path to the Democratic nomination is a tight one .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"The party awards its delegates on a proportional basis ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"so there are no must-win states","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"where he can place big bets the way","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Republicans have .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"He 'll have to win on the coasts","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"-- and that includes New York and its surrounding territory .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"At a rowdy Monday evening rally in Milwaukee , Sanders talked repeatedly about `` momentum ''","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"-- touting poll results , his growth from 2015 and a string of recent victories .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"`` Tomorrow ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"if there is a good turnout here in Wisconsin ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"if there is a record-breaking turnout here in Wisconsin ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"we are going to win here as well , ''","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"JUST WATCHED Sanders :","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"Clinton nervous about losing New York primary","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"MUST WATCH Sanders :","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"Clinton nervous about losing New York primary 04:58","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Clinton 's campaign has downplayed the Wisconsin primary for weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"arguing","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"that the state 's results wo n't tip the delegate count significantly in either direction .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"The former secretary of state was n't even in Wisconsin on Monday","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"-- instead campaigning in New York ,","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"where she faces a closer-than-expected contest in two weeks .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Obviously Clinton would be delighted with a win ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"but no matter what , she will leave Wisconsin with a clear delegate lead .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"But , like Michigan in early March , the state could also leave her with a tougher-than-expected primary on her hands and in a position","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"to explain to backers","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"why she ca n't put the self-described democratic socialist away .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"How Sanders fares","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"when it comes to delegates","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"MUST WATCH How Sanders fares","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"when it comes to delegates","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"03:58","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"For more than a month , Clinton has tried to shift her attention to Republicans and the general election .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"Yet much like Clinton against then-Sen. Barack Obama in 2008 , Sanders ' persistent presence wo n't allow it .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"Clinton campaign manager Robby Mook is telling supporters not to worry .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"In a memo","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"posted on Medium Monday evening ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Mook wrote :","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"`` Sanders has to win the four remaining delegate-rich primaries","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"-- New York , Pennsylvania , California , and New Jersey --","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"with roughly 60 % of the vote .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"To put that in perspective :","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"Sanders has thus far won only two primaries with that margin :","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"Vermont and New Hampshire . ''","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"Ohio Gov . John Kasich has still won only a single state","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"-- his own .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"And he 's increasingly under pressure from both Trump and Cruz ,","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"who are angling behind the scenes for GOP convention rules","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"that would keep him off the first ballot there , and publicly for him to depart the race .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"Donald Trump :","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"John Kasich hurting me more than Ted Cruz","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"MUST WATCH Donald Trump :","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"John Kasich hurting me more than Ted Cruz","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"02:27","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"`` He ought to get the hell out , honestly , ''","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"Trump said Monday in La Crosse .","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"He compared Kasich to Jeb Bush , Florida Sen. Marco Rubio and Kentucky Sen. Rand Paul","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"-- `` every single candidate","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"that went out","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"and worked hard ,","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"that frankly , in most cases , have done much better than Kasich . ''","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"`` He 's just a stubborn guy , ''","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"Trump said of Kasich .","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"`` He 's stubborn .","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"He does n't want to leave . ''","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"Wisconsin , just like Michigan and Illinois before it , is the sort of state","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"where Kasich ought to have a strong showing .","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"Public polls have showed him within striking distance of Trump for second place","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"-- and finishing ahead of Trump would be a major boost .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":367,"left":186,"right":366,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":185,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":366,"left":269,"right":365,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":187,"right":268,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":187,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":198,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":190,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":189,"right":8,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":188,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":192,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare